data.description: Welcome Home for The Holidays!  This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence is a perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. Nestled in a desirable neighborhood of Penn Acers which even features a community pool, this property boasts a spacious interior, a full basement, and a generously sized yard. As you step through the front door, you're greeted by a warm and inviting living space that seamlessly connects the family room, dining area, and kitchen. The layout is perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quality family time. The kitchen features modern appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient breakfast bar. Upstairs, you'll find four bedrooms, each thoughtfully designed to provide comfort and privacy. The primary bedroom is complete with an en-suite bathroom and ample closet space. The remaining bedrooms are versatile, suitable for guests, a home office, or a growing family. The Full Basement adds another dimension to this already spacious home, offering endless possibilities for a recreation room, home gym, or additional storage. Step outside into the expansive yard, whether you host summer barbecues, gardening, or simply relaxing in the fresh air, this yard provides the perfect backdrop for creating lasting memories. Conveniently located near major highways, shopping centers, and eateries and within  walking distance from near by schools.  This home is  not just a residence but a lifestyle upgrade, it's time to make this house your home. Schedule a showing today this home wont last!
